  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">there are other women
who want to say

         me too

but can't

they sit at home

minding the children
of women who march

      &amp; hoping to god

the husbands 
       of those women

do not arrive home
  first</p>

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">The Tories and the DUP have just voted through cuts to free school meals in England.

The Tories bought the DUP's support by excluding Northern Ireland from these cuts.

A disgraceful tactic which is playing politics with the health of our children.<a href="https://t.co/3PhbHl0iB2" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/entry/free-school-meal-eligibility-cuts-go-ahead-after-tory-mps-vote-for-universal-credit-changes-dup-childcare-vouchers-six-month-delay_uk_5aa816a4e4b0a09afeae9d85" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/entry/free-school-meal-eligibility-cuts-go-ahead-after-tory-mps-vote-for-universal-credit-changes-dup-childcare-vouchers-six-month-delay_uk_5aa816a4e4b0a09afeae9d85"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="js-display-url">huffingtonpost.co.uk/entry/free-sch</span><span class="invisible">ool-meal-eligibility-cuts-go-ahead-after-tory-mps-vote-for-universal-credit-changes-dup-childcare-vouchers-six-month-delay_uk_5aa816a4e4b0a09afeae9d85</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

    <a class="QuoteTweet-link js-nav" href="/guardian/status/935138240511860736" data-conversation-id="935138240511860736" aria-hidden="true">
    </a>
    <div class="QuoteTweet-innerContainer u-cf js-permalink js-media-container" data-item-id="935138240511860736" data-item-type="tweet" data-screen-name="guardian" data-user-id="87818409" href="/guardian/status/935138240511860736" data-conversation-id="935138240511860736" tabindex="0">

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Brilliant afternoon in Parliament at the screening of <a href="/hashtag/dispossessionfilm?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>dispossessionfilm</b></a> . <a href="/CarolineLucas" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="80802900"><s>@</s><b>CarolineLucas</b></a> gave the opening note. Followed by a Q&amp;A with <a href="/sianberry" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="477802917"><s>@</s><b>sianberry</b></a>, <a href="/sng_paul" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="2196053491"><s>@</s><b>sng_paul</b></a>, Chantal Lee and Toby Lloyd. Lively debate about social housing crisis, demolition of estates and treatment of tenants.<a href="https://t.co/Ustjl4UhO9" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/Ustjl4UhO9</a></p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Chantal Lee Retweeted Sherwood Labour</p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">I hate seeing the 'c' word in tweets, it's offensive and unnecessary. However, I can just about stomach it if people shorten it to 'Tory'.</p>
